    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab><note>Il <rs key="#Princeps">principe</rs>
                            <persName key="#Princeps" ref="#people/303">Arechi II</persName> offre
                            al monastero di S. Sofia di <placeName key="#Cities" ref="#places/110"
                                >Benevento</placeName> (prosegue l'elenco iniziato con il doc.
                            3535):</note></ab> <ab>(…) [46] Nec non et in <placeName ref="#places/700"
                            key="#Uncertain_tradition #Cities #Houses #Fiscal_property"
                            >Helarino</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Houses">casas</rs> de <rs key="#Specialized_workers"
                            >caballariis</rs> cum <rs key="#Horses">caballos</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Specialized_workers">stodariis</rs>, hi sunt <rs key="#Houses"
                            >casa</rs> que regitur per <name ref="Ursus">Ursus</name> cum uxore et
                        filiis suis et omnibus sibi pertinentibus, <rs key="#Houses">casa</rs> que
                        regitur per <name ref="Lupus">Lupu</name> et <name ref="Fuscillus"
                            >Fuscillu</name> germanos cum uxoribus et filiis et omnibus sibi
                        pertinentibus, <rs key="#Houses">casa</rs> que regitur per <name
                            ref="Widoaldus">Vitoaldu</name> cum uxore et filiis et omnibus sibi
                        pertinentibus, <rs key="#Houses">casa</rs> que regitur per <name
                            ref="Iohannes">Iohannem</name> cum uxore et filiis et omnibus sibi
                        pertinentibus, <rs key="#Houses">casa</rs> que regitur per <name
                            ref="Iustulus">Iustulu</name> et <name ref="Gaudiosus">Gaudioso</name>
                        germanos cum omnibus sibi pertinentibus, secundum qualiter hec omnia, <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">pascua</rs>, <rs key="#Landed_possessions"
                            >clausuria</rs>, <rs key="#Forests">silvas</rs>, <rs key="#Wine"
                            >vineas</rs>, <rs key="#Landed_possessions">prata</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">campos</rs>, mobilia immobilia quantum ipsi
                            <rs key="#Slave_labour #Slave">servi</rs> possidere visi sunt et <rs
                            key="#Textual_occurrence #Mention #Palatium">ad nostram potestatem
                            pertinuerunt</rs>, omnia in integrum <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/85"
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Forests #Wine #Horses #Slave_labour #Agricultural_workers #Specialized_workers #Monasteries"
                            >Sancte Sophie</orgName>
                        <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Horses #Slave_labour #Specialized_workers #Monasteries #Slave"
                            >monasterio</rs> concessimus possidendum. (…)</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
